  "detailed_description": "In Doctor Cat you will one day live in a society of cats! Step into the shoes of Doctor Cat, a renowned psychologist, and take care of cute patient cats by discovering their stories and helping them overcome their traumas.<br><br>Complete <strong>jigsaws based on your patients' stories</strong> to unlock each of their stories<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472870/extras/2e16f0cda6660e02ea7020d0df00e9f7.poster.avif?t=1729198617\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472870/extras/2e16f0cda6660e02ea7020d0df00e9f7.webm?t=1729198617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472870/extras/2e16f0cda6660e02ea7020d0df00e9f7.mp4?t=1729198617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Read stories based on <strong>real trauma</strong> and reflect on your learnings<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472870/extras/d69a8a746bc9a78c819e74a9cf1596bb.poster.avif?t=1729198617\" width=600 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472870/extras/d69a8a746bc9a78c819e74a9cf1596bb.webm?t=1729198617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>12 cats </strong>with captivating stories;<br></li><li><strong>12 jigsaws</strong> based on your patients' stories;<br></li><li>Calm and relaxing music to make your experience better;<br></li><li>Minimal and cartoon arts;<br></li><li>Easy Mode 6x6, Normal Mode 8x8 and Hard Mode 10x10;<br></li><li>Gallery that unlocks a <strong>more difficult mode</strong> for your already finished levels;<br></li><li>Jigsaws <strong>randomly generated</strong> to replay as many times as you want;</li></ul><br>Will you be able to complete all the jigsaws and take care of all your patients trauma?",
